{"tid":1467154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地個日講好左架 係咪？","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:34.000Z","uid":209700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef21f8c5f8612420b51d1a2133d477dd449b3594","tid":1467154,"uid":209700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">有朝一日 我地可以除底口罩相見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地唔記得左啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解郁d就話放棄<br />\n郁d就話輸 <br />\n<br />\n點解啊... 我地唔係約好左架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只係今次做得唔好姐<br />\n下次咪改過囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兄弟間有爭吵好正常<br />\n但係我地永遠都係同一條心架嘛 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不指責</span></span>"},{"pid":"170c1ea52a763ef01ea48f4118e9f945d0edc538","tid":1467154,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不分化不割蓆</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">團結就是力量</span></span>"},{"pid":"ad0328661f9c4123c8534e1f30cb0ad3f2dc592a","tid":1467154,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:58.000Z","msg":"和理非 取消黑衫行動 勇武就無左保護 鬼亦無咁多機會滲透<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定要支持 勇武就無左保護 自然要勇武休息下<br />\n咁鬼既滲透亦無左機會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係 講到明有下場既就全民黑衫 （例如免費過海之類）<br />\n<br />\n機場只宣傳 同控制人流 有人搞事就 比泛民 等泛民開記者會<br />\n<br />\n幫手講佢係鬼 <br />\n<br />\n另外唔建議帶口罩 和理非活動係要一家大細都可以參與"},{"pid":"55cef7d1b4e0df6b11e47eb713dcb2babb20dc61","tid":1467154,"uid":199911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:10:19.000Z","msg":"可愛的香港人&hellip; 唔好俾憤怒蒙敝理智 勿忘初衷<br />\n我地爭取嘅五大訴求 為咁多位義士討回公道<br />\n捉鬼黎打 阻住救護 真係無補於事<br />\n但話咗不分化 都不割蓆 <br />\n每次都有吸取到嘅經驗 我地下次做得更好!<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a312e899b7cee22cd88964f24ada476291799fa2","tid":1467154,"uid":209700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:07.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得<br />\n個六位已經永遠離我們而去既手足<br />\n6月12比人射中眼既義士<br />\n7月1衝日立法會而需要離開香港既幾十位義士<br />\n8月11日比人眼盲眼既女仔<br />\n仲有700幾十位 比人拉左既手足"},{"pid":"fc3587c74d73870400e224413ffa3d603cd8bbde","tid":1467154,"uid":209700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:04.000Z","msg":"我地發左咁多日夢<br />\n經歷左咁多野<br />\n咁辛苦先行到依一步<br />\n大家甘心咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WSQ1OUZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWSQ1OUZ.png&h=030db381&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Sb8tU0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Sb8tU0.jpg&h=dae1efd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3wn32e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3wn32e2.jpg&h=887fff8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMcfTmL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMcfTmL.jpg&h=de6f21eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/52uqv8y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F52uqv8y.jpg&h=430aa01c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g0B4MGU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg0B4MGU.png&h=4ed07a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CTPYQ8B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCTPYQ8B.png&h=4bc7c08a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQ0dE2d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQ0dE2d.png&h=d452a18f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9df8646b742a5b0465ed4feedc61f92af6cef60d","tid":1467154,"uid":209700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}